0advisable%20and%20you%20should%20make%20every%20effort%20possible%20to%20clear%20U.S.%20customs%20before%2012%3A00%20a.m.%20EDT%20(9%3A00%20p.m.%20PDT)%20on%20Sunday%2C%20September%2021%2C%202025.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAt%20this%20time%2C%20if%20you%20have%20an%20H-1B%20or%20H-4%20status%20and%20are%20unable%20to%20return%20before%20the%20deadline%2C%20we%20advise%20that%20you%20do%20not%20attempt%20to%20enter%20the%20U.S.%20until%20further%20guidance%20is%20provided.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f8f8a2e-ef97-4845-8fb3-371f69518146%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIMPORTANT%20ADVISORY%3A%20New%20travel%20restriction%20for%20H-1B%20visa%20holders%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Updated%20at%206%3A04%20pm%20pacific%20with%20the%20intake%20form%20for%20those%20outside%20of%20the%20U.S.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHi%20all--We%20have%20now%20reviewed%20the%20actual%20text%20of%20today's%20Presidential%20Proclamation%20on%20H-1B%20visas%2C%20which%20you%20can%20find%20here%3A%20Restriction%20on%20Entry%20of%20Certain%20Nonimmigrant%20Workers%20%E2%80%94%20The%20White%20House.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHere's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFirst%2C%20the%20proclamation%20is%20structured%20as%20a%20travel%20restriction.%20Beginning%20at%2012%3A01%20am%20eastern%20time%20on%20September%2021%2C%202025%20(so%2C%209%3A01%20pm%20Pacific%20time%20tomorrow)%2C%20individuals%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20enter%2Freturn%20to%20the%20U.S.%20in%20H-1B%20status%20unless%20their%20petition%20has%20an%20additional%20%24100%2C000%20payment%20associated%20with%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhat%20you%20need%20to%20do%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20in%20H-1B%20status%20and%20are%20in%20the%20U.S.%2C%20you%20should%20remain%20in%20the%20U.S.%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20We%20know%20this%20may%20interrupt%20your%20travel%20plans.%20But%20the%20critical%20thing%20is%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20U.S.%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20being%20denied%20reentry.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhile%20the%20proclamation%20doesn't%20reference%20H-4%20dependents%2C%20we%20also%20recommend%20that%20H-4s%20remain%20in%20the%20U.S.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20in%20H-1B%20or%20H-4%20status%20and%20are%20currently%20outside%20the%20U.S.%2C%20we%20strongly%20recommend%20that%20you%20do%20what%20you%20can%20to%20return%20to%20the%20U.S.%20tomorrow%20before%20the%20deadline.%20The%20Proclamation%20was%20released%20within%20the%20last%2030%20minutes%2C%20so%20we%20realize%20that%20there%20isn't%20much%20time%20to%20make%20sudden%20travel%20arrangements.%20But%20again%2C%20we%20strongly%20encourage%20you%20to%20do%20your%20best%20to%20return.%20If%20you%20are%20not%20able%20to%20return%2C%20please%20use%20this%20form%20to%20let%20us%20know%20about%20your%20situation.%20Please%20only%20complete%20that%20form%20if%20you%20are%20outside%20of%20the%20U.S.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20follow%20up%20with%20each%20individual%20and%20provide%20support%20and%20guidance%20as%20they%20try%20to%20return%20within%20the%20next%2028%20hours.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20will%20also%20be%20reaching%20out%20to%20everyone%20by%20email%20later%20today%20to%20make%20sure%20everyone%20is%20aware.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20proclamation%20does%20not%20impact%20any%20other%20visa%20statuses.%20(Note%2C%20we%20have%20started%20receiving%20emails%20from%20people%20in%20other%20statuses%20like%20L-1%20and%20TN%20asking%20about%20impacts.%20I'll%20reiterate%20that%20this%20does%20not%20impact%20people%20in%20other%20statuses.%20If%20you%20refrain%20from%20sending%20in%20questions%20asking%20about%20that%2C%20it%20will%20help%20us%20divert%20our%20resources%20to%20help%20those%20who%20are%20impacted.%20Thanks!)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThere%20is%20other%20content%20in%20the%20proclamation%20about%20the%20pause%20in%20processing%20H-1B%20petitions%20for%20individuals%20who%20are%20outside%20the%20U.S.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20we%20do%20not%20interpret%20this%20to%20immediately%20impact%20extensions%20of%20H-1B%20status%20or%20changes%20of%20status%20to%20H-1B%20as%20long%20as%20you%20are%20currently%20in%20the%20U.S.%20We'll%20share%20more%20about%20that%20later.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20know%20these%20developments%20are%20creating%20anxiety%20and%20uncertainty%20for%20many%20of%20you.%20While%20we%20don't%20have%20all%20of%20the%20answers%20right%20now%2C%20we%20ask%20that%20you%20prioritize%20the%20recommendations%20above.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Amazon%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-memos-sent-big-tech-trump-h-1b-changes-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758392310000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cea97357d362d375e8914b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-memos-sent-big-tech-trump-h-1b-changes-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Trump%20administration%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20it%20would%20raise%20application%20fees%20for%20the%20H-1B%20visa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pdixit%40insider.com%20(Pranav%20Dixit%2CHugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A334%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-memos-sent-big-tech-trump-h-1b-changes-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20Starbucks'%20crackdown%20on%20cup%20notes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Starbucks%20cup%20with%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BMateusz%26quot%3B%20written%20on%20it%20in%20black%20Sharpie%5C%2