22268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20raising%20her%20kids%20in%20Wales.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20downside%20of%20international%20chats%20is%20the%20time%20difference.%20We%20are%20five%20hours%20ahead%20here%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20proves%20tricky%20during%20the%20week.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20my%20mom%20is%20out%20of%20work%2C%20we%20typically%20go%20to%20bed.%20But%20we've%20learned%20the%20days%20and%20times%20that%20work%20and%20take%20full%20advantage%20of%20those%20times%20to%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20eldest%20son%20recently%20got%20a%20phone%20and%20has%20gotten%20in%20on%20the%20texting%20fun.%20He%20loves%20being%20able%20to%20message%20the%20family%20about%20very%20random%20bits%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0587574-8a93-4614-9dad-b49a7d6a8cfa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20parents%20send%20the%20kids%20presents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20ways%20my%20parents%20have%20stayed%20connected%20to%20our%20boys%20is%20through%20presents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20first%2C%20this%20annoyed%20me.%20We%20have%20a%20tiny%20house%20with%20no%20extra%20space.%20Stuff%20sprawls%20out%20of%20every%20corner.%20When%20packages%20would%20come%20%E2%80%94%20on%20birthdays%2C%20holidays%2C%20and%20even%20just%20random%20days%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20sigh%2C%20wondering%20where%20I'd%20put%20them%20once%20opened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20my%20mom%20recently%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20my%20way%20of%20showing%20them%20I%20am%20thinking%20about%20them%20when%20I%20can't%20be%20close.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20I've%20not%20complained%2C%20but%20welcomed%20the%20gifts%20as%20connection%20points%2C%20even%20if%20they%20do%20fill%20our%20house%20to%20overflowing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e77de4c-4cca-4d9f-b67a-f0cd80fd88aa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20visit%20my%20family%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20having%20kids%2C%20I%20flew%20over%20once%20a%20year%20to%20visit.%20With%20my%20first%20two%2C%20I%20continued%20trying%20to%20get%20over%20once%20a%20year%2C%20but%20it%20became%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20manage%20both%20the%20practicalities%20of%20traveling%20with%20young%20children%20and%20the%20costs%20of%20plane%20tickets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20I%20had%20three%20kids%2C%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20which%20halted%20our%20travel%20for%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20that%20travelling%20back%20is%20an%20option%2C%20my%20kids%20are%20older%20%E2%80%94%2011%2C%209%2C%20and%206%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20much%20easier%20to%20travel%20distances%20with.%20They%20just%20watch%20TV%20or%20play%20on%20tablets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20kids%20might%20be%20easy%20to%20travel%20with%2C%20but%20the%20price%20of%20international%20travel%20is%20astronomical.%20We%20save%20up%20for%20it%20as%20a%20normal%20part%20of%20our%20budgeting%2C%20and%20my%20family%20occasionally%20offers%20to%20help%20by%20buying%20tickets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDifferent%20family%20members%20also%20try%20to%20visit%20us%20here%20too.%20Recently%2C%20my%20sister%20actually%20moved%20to%20London%2C%20about%20four%20hours%20from%20us%2C%20so%20we%20see%20her%20more%20often%2C%20which%20has%20been%20absolutely%20lovely%20for%20my%20boys%20and%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cfcb81b2-6743-4669-8b44-67aae86d561d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20worry%20about%20my%20aging%20parents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20consider%20what%20maintaining%20connection%20with%20family%20will%20look%20like%20in%20the%20future%2C%20I%20worry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20parents%20certainly%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20visit%20us%20when%20they%20are%20in%20their%2080s%2C%20which%20means%20it%20will%20always%20be%20us%20going%20there%20for%20visits%20(money%2C%20money).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20who%20is%20going%20to%20take%20care%20of%20them%20as%20their%20health%20declines%3F%20I%20genuinely%20think%20this%20might%20be%20the%20hardest%20part%20of%20living%20in%20a%20different%20country%20than%20they%20are.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20prepare%2C%20I'm%20putting%20money%20away%20so%20I%20can%20quickly%20book%20a%20plane%20ticket%20if%20they%20need%20me.%20In%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20also%20considering%20what%20we%20need%20to%20organize%20(visas%20and%20money)%20so%20we%20can%20live%20short-term%20in%20the%20US%20to%20help%20out%20as%20my%20parents%20age.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20I%20don't%20regret%20leaving%20my%20family%20to%20marry%20and%20raise%20my%20family%20in%20a%20different%20country%2C%20it%20has%20made%20life%20more%20complicated%20and%20costly%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20known%2C%20so%20I%20could%20have%20been%20better%20prepared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-the-us-to-wales-fourteen-years-ago-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758387061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c9971d57d362d375e84269%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-the-us-to-wales-fourteen-years-ago-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20didn't%20consider%20how%20hard%20it%20would%20be%20to%20stay%20close%20to%20my%20family%20when%20I%20moved.%20Now%20I%20have%20three%20kids%20and%20I%20have%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20visit%20every%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider