visit%20again%20and%20again%2C%20but%20just%20one%20I%20wouldn't%20rush%20back%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDuring%20my%20visit%2C%20I%20found%20Edinburgh%20Castle%20to%20be%20overcrowded%20and%20underwhelming.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224873%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Edinburgh%20Castle%20in%20Scotland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c82f0df9db348adc0b7995%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223655%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaption%3Cp%3EWirestock%20Creators%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-visit-scotland-haunted-edinburgh-castle-photos-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEdinburgh%20Castle%3C%2Fa%3E%20looks%20impressive%20perched%20atop%20Castle%20Rock%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20particularly%20pretty%20when%20viewed%20from%20Princes%20Street%20Gardens%20or%20the%20Vennel%20%E2%80%94%20I%20found%20the%20inside%20to%20be%20a%20letdown%20when%20I%20last%20visited%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20castle%20is%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotland-best-places-non-tourist-areas-you-should-visit-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EScotland's%20most%20popular%20tourist%20attractions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20felt%20unpleasantly%20busy.%20After%20waiting%20in%20a%2020-minute%20line%20to%20see%20the%20Crown%20Jewels%2C%20I%20found%20the%20crown%2C%20sword%2C%20and%20scepter%20to%20be%20underwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20anyone%20hoping%20to%20see%20the%20Stone%20of%20Destiny%20%E2%80%94%20upon%20which%20monarchs%20are%20still%20crowned%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20disappointed.%20I%20was%20sad%20to%20learn%20that%20the%20historic%20block%20of%20sandstone%20was%20moved%20to%20the%20Perth%20Museum%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20found%20very%20little%20information%20on%20placards%20about%20the%20castle's%