-movies-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehorror%20movie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Cade%20travels%20to%20White's%20compound%20to%20audition%20for%20the%20quarterback%20job.%20If%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20he%20is%20guaranteed%20a%20contract%20to%20take%20White's%20spot%20on%20the%20team.%20But%20it's%20quickly%20revealed%20that%20White's%20training%20is%20demented%2C%20leaving%20Cade%20bloodied%20and%20questioning%20his%20sanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20all%20culminates%20in%20a%20blood-spattered%20ending%20that%20Tipping%20says%20took%20many%20passes%20in%20the%20edit%20room%20to%20get%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marlon%20Wayans%20and%20Tyriq%20Withers%20flexing%20their%20muscles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cbfb7957d362d375e86532%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22789%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarlon%20Wayans%20and%20Tyriq%20Withers%20in%20%26quot%3BHim.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EUniversal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETipping%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20goal%20for%20the%20ending%20was%20to%20make%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20beat%20the%20weird%2C%20crazy%20shit%20that%20just%20came%20before%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conclusion%20comes%20in%20two%20parts.%20First%2C%20Cade%20finds%20White%20tucked%20away%20in%20his%20%26quot%3Bfilm%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20just%20a%20room%20where%20he%20sits%20and%20watches%20video%20of%20a%20crowd%20cheering%20his%20name.%20White%20tells%20Cade%20that%20he's%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20up%20his%20spot%20on%20the%20team%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20the%20two%20having%20an%20all-out%20brawl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20we%20were%20building%20towards%20this%20very%20ritualistic%20film%20room%20where%20they%20have%20their%20gladiator%20fight%20to%20the%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20Tipping%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20intentional%20to%20keep%20the%20fight%20in%20the%20film%20room%20all%20fists.%20Beating%20each%20other's%20asses%20and%20colliding%20and%20snapping%20elbows.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Cade%20kills%20White%20by%20beating%20him%20to%20a%20bloody%20pulp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20it%20becomes%2C%20how%20do%20you%20beat%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20Tipping%20said%20of%20building%20out%20the%20second%20part%20of%20the%20ending.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20we%20construct%20this%20so%20that%20it%20becomes%20full%20slasher%2C%20full%20promise%20of%20the%20genre%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECade%20leaves%20the%20film%20room%20and%20walks%20onto%20a%20makeshift%20football%20field.%20The%20team's%20unnamed%20owner%20(Richard%20Lippert)%2C%20Cade's%20agent%20(Tim%20Heidecker)%2C%20and%20White's%20wife%20Elsie%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjulia-fox-style-most-daring-fashion-looks-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJulia%20Fox%3C%2Fa%3E)%20are%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20field%20ready%20for%20Cade%20to%20come%20sign%20the%20contract.%20Between%20them%20is%20a%20giant%20pagan-like%20symbol%20and%20a%20buff%20man%20holding%20a%20sword%20surrounded%20by%20cheerleaders%20and%20a%20marching%20band.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20it%20to%20feel%20like%20this%20rite%20of%20passage%2C%20so%20I%20was%20pulling%20imagery%20from%20Super%20Bowls%20and%20the%20pomp%20and%20circumstance%20and%20the%20performative%20absurdity%2C%20but%C2%A0I%20also%20wanted%20to%20introduce%20a%20sword%20and%20the%20ritualistic%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20Tipping%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tyriq%20Withers%20holding%20a%20football%20next%20to%20someone%20with%20a%20hammer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cbfc03183847aa39d70122%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BHim.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EUniversal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20the%20big%20reveal%20happens%3A%20Cade's%20whole%20life%20has%20been%20leading%20up%20to%20this%20moment.%20When%20he%20was%20a%20child%2C%20his%20late%20father%20made%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20team's%20owner%20for%20him%20to%20one%20day%20become%20his%20star%20quarterback.%20Even%20Cade's%20attack%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20which%20left%20him%20with%20a%20head%20injury%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20as%20it%20made%20Cade's%20draft%20status%20questionable%20and%20therefore%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20the%20owner%20to%20sign%20him.%20This%20should%20be%20Cade's%20moment%20of%20triumph%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20see%20it%20that%20way.%20After%20the%20experience%20training%20with%20White%2C%20he%20doesn't%20want%20any%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20leads%20Cade%20on%20a%20bloody%20rampage%2C%20killing%20everyone%20in%20sight%20in%20a%20sadistic%20manner%20(yes%2C%20he%20puts%20that%20sword%20to%20use)%20until%20he's%20left%20alone%20on%20the%20field%20in%20blood-soaked%20ecstasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETipping%20said%20he%20and%20editor%20Taylor%20Joy%20Mason%20made%2040%20different%20versions%20of%20the%20ending%2C%20and%20often%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcool-things-about-jordan-peele-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJordan%20Peele%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who's%20a%20producer%20on%20the%20movie%20through%20his%20Monkeypaw%20Productions%2C%20as%20a%20fresh%20set%20of%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20Tipping%20Tyriq%20Withers%20Jordan%20Peele%20and%20Marlon%20Wayans%20standing%20next%20to%20each%20other%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cbfcbe57d362d375e8653e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Justin%20Tipping%2C%20Tyriq%20Withers%2C%20Jordan%20Peele%2C%20and%20Marlon%20Wayans%20on%20the%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BHim.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EParrish%20Lewis%2FUniv